ActNunavut Act
SubjectTransfer to the Commissioner of Nunavut (approximately 2.39 hectares)
PrecisOrder transfering to the COMMISSIONER OF NUNAVUT, in perpetuity, the administration and control of a surveyed parcel of land comprising the bed of a body of water within a pond (approximatively 2.39 hectares), within the municipal boundaries of the hamlet of Pond Inlet.
